      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne ¶ 1/12/73 ¶  ¶ The expenditure of £100, dear Mr Bentham, for the next volume ¶ The Victorian Government's payment to Bentham for his work onFlora australiensiswasincluded in the 'AdditionalE...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">73.12.01a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To George Bentham</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Kew correspondence, Australia, Mueller, 1871-81, f. 132.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1/12/73</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The expenditure of £100, dear Mr Bentham, for the next volume<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">The Victorian Government's payment to Bentham for his work on<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #000000; ">Flora australiensis<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">was</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #000000; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">included in the 'Additional</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #000000; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">Estimates for 1873-4', approved<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">on<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">2</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">9</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>October 1873 (Victoria,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #000000; ">Votes and proceedings of the Legislative Assembly</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #000000; ">session 1873</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">vol</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">pp</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">229</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">).</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has been authorized formally. If you get no intimation of its being placed at your disposal already by this mail, you will be sure to get such by the next, or if not you need only place yourself in communication with the hon. Archibald Michie, Q.C., the present Agent General of Victoria in London.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I cannot imagine what became of the Australian specimens of Bischoffia Javanic[a]<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>and at least one Aporosa.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See G.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Bentham to M, 24 September 1873.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Perhaps they were mislaid here, what will be pardonable through the narrowness of space here</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Let me trust that you health is firm. I was much gladdened when I saw by last mail, that the 6th vol. had been brought to a conclusion by your unceasing exertions.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">See G. Bentham to M, 24 September 1873.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As yet I have no bill of loading of the case with Haemodoraceae &amp;c. Will you kindly enquire by what ship the return sending of that portion of the collection has been effected.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3347in; text-indent: -0.3347in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation, possibly by Hooker: '<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>K[osciusko] | July'. Cf. G. Bentham to M, 27 August 1873: 'I trust that you will have received safe the Monocotyledons which were sent I believe by the Kosciusko'.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #000000; ">Kosciusko</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>began to unload cargo at Williamstown on 14 October 1873 (</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #000000; ">Argus</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">, 15 October 1873, p. 4). <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The case was presumably waiting to be collected when M wrote.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully always<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Aporosa</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Bischoffia Javanica</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Haemodoraceae<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
